OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777983071
OL,3,CDriver seriously injured as police
OL,4,Cpursuit ends in crash outside airport
OL,6,FEarly morning travellers at a major UK
OL,7,Fairport faced major disruption after a
OL,8,Fpolice pursuit ended in a serious
OL,9,Fcrash outside the main terminal.
OL,11,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,12,Fconfirmed that the driver of a vehicle
OL,13,Fbeing pursued by officers was taken to
OL,14,Fhospital with serious injuries
OL,15,Ffollowing the collision at Manchester
OL,16,FAirport on Tuesday, 5 May.
OL,18,FThe incident resulted in the closure
OL,19,Fof the upper forecourt drop-off zone
OL,20,Fat Terminal 2 for three hours while
OL,21,Femergency services attended the scene.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
