PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777983071
OL,3,CDriver seriously injured as police
OL,4,Cpursuit ends in crash outside airport
OL,6,FIn a statement released online at
OL,7,F2:30am, a GMP spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Following a police pursuit, a road
OL,9,Ftraffic collision occurred close to
OL,10,FTerminal 2 at Manchester Airport.
OL,12,F"The driver of the vehicle has been
OL,13,Ftaken to hospital with serious
OL,14,Finjuries. Due to the location of the
OL,15,Fcollision, disruption is expected for
OL,16,Fairport passengers."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
