OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777983071
OL,3,CDriver seriously injured as police
OL,4,Cpursuit ends in crash outside airport
OL,6,FThe closure caused significant issues
OL,7,Ffor passengers heading to Terminal 2,
OL,8,Fwhich now serves as the airport's main
OL,9,Fhub for all departures, with the
OL,10,Fexception of Ryanair.
OL,12,FDuring the height of the disruption,
OL,13,Fairport officials warned of heavy
OL,14,Fcongestion as all traffic was diverted.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for Manchester Airport
OL,17,Fsaid earlier this morning: "Please be
OL,18,Faware: due to a road traffic
OL,19,Fcollision, the upper forecourt of
OL,20,FTerminal 2 is closed until further
OL,21,Fnotice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
