OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777983071
OL,3,CDriver seriously injured as police
OL,4,Cpursuit ends in crash outside airport
OL,6,F"All drivers are being redirected to
OL,7,Fthe lower forecourt. As a result,
OL,8,Fcongestion on the site is expected and
OL,9,Fjourneys are likely to take longer
OL,10,Fthan normal."
OL,12,FThe airport has since confirmed that
OL,13,Fthe scene has been cleared and the
OL,14,Fupper forecourt reopened at
OL,15,Fapproximately 5:30am.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
