CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777983071
OL,3,CDriver seriously injured as police
OL,4,Cpursuit ends in crash outside airport
OL,6,FIn a follow-up post, the airport
OL,7,Fthanked passengers for their
OL,8,Fcooperation, stating: "The upper
OL,9,Fforecourt at Terminal 2 has reopened
OL,10,Ffollowing the earlier road traffic
OL,11,Fcollision.
OL,13,F"We thank people for their patience
OL,14,Fand apologise for any delays."
